Changes for pytextseg package

* 0.0.3  2012-02-25
	- Added fold().
	- Added test cases.

* 0.0.2  2012-02-10
	- Switched to CPython 3.3 style Unicode handling (PEP 393).
	  Python 2.x including "narrow" Unicode implenentation is still 
	  supported.

* 0.0.1  2012-02-04
	- "Wide" Unicode implementation only.
	- Supported Python 3.x.

* 0.0.0  2012-01-29
	- 

